  "name": "Sven Väth",
  "profile": "Sven Väth (born: 26 October 1964 in Obertshausen, Germany), is one of Germany's most enduring and internationally known DJs / producers. Since he began DJ'ing at the famous [url=https://www.discogs.com/label/611374]Dorian Gray[/url] club at the age of 18, he co-founded trendsetting labels [l=Eye Q Records], [l=Harthouse] and [l=Cocoon Recordings]; he ran the clubs [url=https://www.discogs.com/label/1863909]OMEN[/url] and Cocoon Club. He's been considered the #1 German DJ for ages, by many. One of his trademarks are his vinyl-only marathon sets.",
